    <string name="msg_about">
        <![CDATA[
        <html>
            <body>
        <h2 align="center">Emulator of \"Elektronika  MK 61\" and
        \"Elektronika MK-54\" programmable calculators</h2>

        <h4 align="center">Version: {0}</h4>

        <p>
        Usage hints:
        <ul>
        <li> to open the Info panel use menu or tap on the <b>ⓘ</b> button</li>
        <li> Tap the \"Вкл\" label to open menu</li>
        <li> ouch indicator to toggle emulation speed slow/fast</li>
        <li> Long-touch indicator to hide/show switches</li>
        <li> ou can import programms from external files via the \"Import\" menu. More information about import
        <a href="https://xvadim.github.io/xbasoft//pmk/program_package.html">here</a> (on Russian)</li>
        <li> Switch calculator off to select MK 61 or MK-54 in Menu</li>
        <li> Long-touch the \"Электроника МК\" label when calculator turned off to toggle calculator model</li>
        </ul>
        </p>

        <p>Developer: <a href="mailto:vadim.khohlov@gmail.com">Vadim Khohlov</a></p>

        <p>
        Based on <a href="http://code.google.com/p/emu145">emu145</a> project
        by Felix Lazarev
        and <br>
        <a href="https://github.com/cax/pmk-android">pmk-android</a>
        by Stanislav Borutsky\n
        </p>

        <p>
        Project <a href="https://github.com/xvadim/pmk-android">repository</a>.
        </p>

        <p>
        A small  <a href="https://xvadim.github.io/xbasoft//pmk/pmk.html#programs">repository</a> of МК-61/54 progarms.
        </p>

        <p align="center">
        <font size=-1>Support project
        <ul>
            <li><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.xbasoft.pmk_donate">Base donation</a> (0.5$)</li>
            <li><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.xbasoft.pmk_donate.ag">Silver donation</a> (1$)</li>
            <li><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.xbasoft.pmk_donate.au">Gold donation</a> (1.5$)</li>
        </ul>
        </font>
        </p>
        </body>
        </html>
        ]]>
    </string>

