                <h2 align="center">Program description</h2>
                <p>
                A program description can be imported with a program from an external file.
                </p>

                <p>The program description is stored in a <b><i>html</i></b>-file with the same name as the program file.</p>
                <p><a href="https://xvadim.github.io/xbasoft/pmk/program_package.html">Description</a> of the description file.</p>

                <p>
                You can download some МК-programs and descriptions from this
                <a href="https://xvadim.github.io/xbasoft/pmk/pmk.html#programs">repository</a>.
                </p>
            </body>
